Φ(Egregores & IFS Neurophysiology) = σ(individual_parts|collective_egregores) ∘ ρ(self_report|physiological_markers) ∘ λ(blended|unblended) ∘ β(agreement_illusion|authentic_consensus) ∘ δγ(blending_unblending_cycles|detection_renewal) ∘ μ(individual_therapy|group_dynamics) + ε | :neurophysiological_unblending

## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: individual_parts|collective_egregores — The foundational distinction between IFS parts (Managers, Firefighters, Exiles) as individual psychological constructs and egregores as collective thought forms that mimic, amplify, and co-opt those parts; recognizing when a part's activation reflects egregoric influence rather than personal history
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: self_report|physiological_markers — Relating subjective self-report (how one feels, what one believes) to objective neurophysiological markers (EEG beta elevation, low HRV, high GSR) that indicate egregore blending; the relational mapping between inner experience and measurable biological signature
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: blended|unblended — Transforming blended egregore-influenced states (where collective thought forms drive individual parts) into unblended Self-led awareness; unblending shows increased HRV, alpha/theta power, and gamma coherence as physiological signatures of liberation from egregoric capture
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: agreement_illusion|authentic_consensus — The developmental trajectory from agreement illusion (where egregoric influence produces apparent unanimity) to authentic consensus in group settings; maturation requires distinguishing genuine collective wisdom from egregore-driven conformity
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: blending_unblending_cycles|detection_renewal — The cycling between blending phases (egregoric capture detected through physiological markers) and unblending phases (Self-energy restored through biofeedback-supported practice); renewal requires ongoing detection and release
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: individual_therapy|group_dynamics — The structural contrast between individual IFS therapy (working with personal parts) and group dynamics that include egregoric dimensions; group biofeedback dashboards as structural tools for detecting collective belief dominance

## Z-State

:neurophysiological_unblending — Egregoric influences on IFS parts are detected through physiological signatures (elevated EEG beta, low HRV, high GSR) and dissolved through biofeedback-supported unblending, revealing authentic Self-energy beneath collective thought form overlay. The Z-state emerges when neurophysiological markers become reliable indicators of egregoric capture and liberation, enabling both individual and group therapeutic processes to distinguish genuine Self-leadership from egregore-driven reactivity.

## Tendency

ρ → 0.85

